---
import RootLayout from '../components/RootLayout.astro';
---

<RootLayout title="Privacy Policy" description="Privacy Policy for Lipi Lekhika" index={false}>
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl px-4 py-12 sm:px-6">
    <h1 class="mb-8 text-4xl font-bold">Privacy Policy</h1>

    <div class="prose prose-invert max-w-none space-y-6">
      <p class="text-lg text-muted-foreground">
        <strong>Last Updated:</strong> January 26, 2026
      </p>

      <section class="space-y-4">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold">Introduction</h2>
        <p>
          Lipi Lekhika ("we", "our", or "the app") is committed to protecting your privacy. This
          Privacy Policy explains how our Android application handles data.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="space-y-4">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold">Data Collection</h2>
        <p>
          <strong>We do NOT collect any personal information.</strong> Lipi Lekhika does not collect,
          store, or share any personally identifiable information such as:
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc space-y-2 pl-6">
          <li>Name, email address, or phone number</li>
          <li>Location data</li>
          <li>Device identifiers (except anonymous analytics identifiers)</li>
          <li>User-generated content or text you write in the app</li>
          <li>Contacts, photos, or any other personal data</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section class="space-y-4">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold">Anonymous Analytics</h2>
        <p>
          We collect anonymous usage analytics through <strong>PostHog</strong>, a third-party
          analytics service. This data is completely anonymous and cannot be used to identify you
          personally. The information collected includes:
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc space-y-2 pl-6">
          <li>App usage patterns (which features are used)</li>
          <li>Screen views and navigation flows</li>
          <li>Device type and operating system version</li>
          <li>App performance metrics (crashes, errors)</li>
          <li>General usage statistics</li>
        </ul>
        <p>
          This anonymous data helps us understand how the app is used and improve its functionality
          and user experience.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="space-y-4">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold">Third-Party Services</h2>
        <p>
          We use PostHog for anonymous analytics. PostHog may collect and process anonymous data as
          described in their privacy policy. You can learn more about PostHog's privacy practices
          at:
          <a
            href="https://posthog.com/privacy"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
            class="text-primary hover:underline"
          >
            https://posthog.com/privacy
          </a>
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="space-y-4">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold">Data Storage</h2>
        <p>
          All your text and preferences are stored locally on your device only. We do not have
          access to this data, and it never leaves your device. You maintain complete control over
          your data.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="space-y-4">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold">Children's Privacy</h2>
        <p>
          Our app does not collect any personal information from anyone, including children under 13
          years of age.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="space-y-4">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold">Changes to This Privacy Policy</h2>
        <p>
          We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Any changes will be posted on this
          page with an updated "Last Updated" date. We encourage you to review this Privacy Policy
          periodically.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="space-y-4">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold">Contact Us</h2>
        <p>
          If you have any questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at:
        </p>
        <p>
          <a
            href="https://github.com/shubhattin/lipilekhika"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
            class="text-primary hover:underline"
          >
            GitHub Repository
          </a>
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="mt-8 rounded-lg border border-border/40 bg-muted/20 p-6">
        <h3 class="mb-2 text-xl font-semibold">Summary</h3>
        <p class="text-muted-foreground">
          <strong>Your privacy is important to us.</strong> Lipi Lekhika does not collect any personal
          information. We only collect anonymous usage statistics to improve the app. All your content
          stays on your device.
        </p>
      </section>
    </div>
  </div>
</RootLayout>
